#!/bin/bash -e
cat <<EOF
This is the elixir builder S2I image:
To use it, install S2I: https://github.com/openshift/source-to-image

Sample invocation:

s2i build git://<source code> elixir-builder <application image>

You can then run the resulting image via:
docker run <application image>

If the Environment Variables `ENABLE_DISTILLERY` and
`DISTILLERY_APP_NAME` are provided, the image will build
and run with distillery.
EOF
